    /// @param vB The second bytes.
    /// @param offB The offset of the second bytes.
    /// @param lenB The length of the second bytes.
    /// @return Positive number if `A > B`, negative number if `A < B`, or zero if `A == B`.
    function compare(
        bytes memory vA,
